OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright or
OL,6,Fclear spells continue as showers die
OL,7,Fduring the evening. Then the rest of
OL,8,Fthe night will be dry but clouding
OL,9,Fover in the south and west later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FDry and bright in the north
OL,12,Fat first. Cloud and rain, some heavy,
OL,13,Fsoon spread northeast. The rain
OL,14,Fbecomes light and patchy during the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOutbreaks
OL,18,Fof locally heavy rain spread northeast
OL,19,FFriday. Bright spells and a few
OL,20,Fshowers on Saturday. Dry and bright on
OL,21,FSunday. Warm in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
